(658, 'project', 'content', 3, 'en', '<p>Since 2021, members of the IT From Union have been working on the issue of smartphone production by a smartphone manufacturer, a member of the IT Prom Union, together with partners, the issues of purchasing components for a smartphone have been worked out. A test assembly of samples was carried out, at the same time, all production features were recorded, including the timing of the assembly of a unit of production. Currently, based on the results obtained, technical issues are being worked out with partners.</p>', '2022-02-04 05:47:08', '2022-02-08 04:56:46'),
