(666, 'project', 'content', 2, 'en', '<p>Members of the IT Prom Union are working on the issue of the production of video cameras in Kazakhstan. The market volume of video cameras in Kazakhstan is about 45 million US dollars. The main importing countries are China - 46%, Russia - 28%, Bulgaria - 9%, Turkey - 4%, Japan - 3%. According to IHS Markit, the global market volume will increase by an average of 15% annually. The researchers stressed that the growth of the market for urban video surveillance systems is due to active investments from large megacities &mdash; such equipment allows you to monitor public safety and reduce crime.</p>', '2022-02-04 05:50:39', '2022-02-08 04:54:22'),
(667, 'project', 'seo_title', 2, 'en', 'Production of video cameras', '2022-02-04 05:50:39', '2022-02-08 04:54:22'),
